- adjust text wrapping with CSS
- minor improvements to the template engine
- properly initialize the `lang' buffer
- pledge(2) the main process
- ensure that -Werror is not used in release tarballs

* galileo 0.2; 2023-03-18
- correct "FastCGI" spelling
- link WAIT_ANY tests in the build
- various improvements to the template engine
- don't rebuild `template' unless strictly needed
- add a navigation bar
- fix styling for consequent blockquotes
- allow to disable the navbar, footer and image preview

* galileo 0.1; 2022-11-12
